---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Studio Mua"
  description="Studio Mua privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal data in compliance with GDPR."
  lang="en"
  noindex={true}
>
  <div class="privacy-container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <section>
      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        Welcome to Studio Mua's Privacy Policy. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your information.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you use our contact form, we collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Name</li>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Preferred meeting type</li>
        <li>Message or inquiry</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <p>We use the collected data to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Respond to your inquiries and questions</li>
        <li>Provide requested services</li>
        <li>Improve the quality of our services</li>
        <li>Communicate with you regarding our services</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>4. Data Protection</h2>
      <p>
        We adopt appropriate security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, alterations, disclosures, or destruction. Your data is processed in accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell, trade, or transfer your personal data to third parties without your consent, except when required by law or necessary to provide requested services.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Object to data processing</li>
        <li>Request restriction of processing</li>
        <li>Request data portability</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Our website does not use tracking cookies. Only technical cookies necessary for the site's functionality may be used.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>8. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with the update date.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or to exercise your rights, you can contact us through the contact form on our website.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: January 2026</p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .privacy-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    color: var(--brown);
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    color: var(--brown);
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--brown);
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  p {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  ul {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-left: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .privacy-container {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    p, ul {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
